  "3179860": {
    "name": "勇者翻翻看",
    "steam_appid": 3179860,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179860/extras/f3cceef41dd0c3f0ec1a0ce97716b846.avif?t=1769855158\" width=616 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >记住桌面上的卡牌位置。将英雄和相应的武器配对以攻击敌人，务必避开陷阱。陷阱会对你造成伤害并跳过你的回合。敌人有自己的攻击计数器，每回合递减，靠近发起攻击。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179860/extras/40a38b30e1dd21b468bfbe93c012e4c5.poster.avif?t=1769855158\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179860/extras/40a38b30e1dd21b468bfbe93c012e4c5.webm?t=1769855158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179860/extras/40a38b30e1dd21b468bfbe93c012e4c5.mp4?t=1769855158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179860/extras/213c0546f0ddc1e0307d31c312dd8e70.avif?t=1769855158\" width=616 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次战斗结束后，你将访问商人的商品，在那里你可以购买新的遗物和消耗品卡牌。遗物具有被动效果，满足特定条件时触发；消耗品则在战斗中帮助你。尝试不同的组合，找到适合你的策略！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179860/extras/ed8e9d7539201c91ccd44e12968c04bc.poster.avif?t=1769855158\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179860/extras/ed8e9d7539201c91ccd44e12968c04bc.webm?t=1769855158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179860/extras/ed8e9d7539201c91ccd44e12968c04bc.mp4?t=1769855158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179860/extras/efb840957a3b21265c404a726066afdf.avif?t=1769855158\" width=616 height=65 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次游戏都会有所不同。敌人、遗物和消耗品都是随机的。你永远不知道下一个房间里会遇到什么。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179860/extras/1c2a42ffc0415965c04f5984400dc72c.poster.avif?t=1769855158\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179860/extras/1c2a42ffc0415965c04f5984400dc72c.webm?t=1769855158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179860/extras/1c2a42ffc0415965c04f5984400dc72c.mp4?t=1769855158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179860/extras/6028b042abd39066f65b8544314388bc.avif?t=1769855158\" width=616 height=65 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在地牢的深处，最后一个房间里，一个无情的Boss在等着你。每次游戏的Boss都可能不同，带来不同的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179860/extras/8b716ec3de8eb5e67bfb401ba899e8b8.poster.avif?t=1769855158\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179860/extras/8b716ec3de8eb5e67bfb401ba899e8b8.webm?t=1769855158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179860/extras/8b716ec3de8eb5e67bfb401ba899e8b8.mp4?t=1769855158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
